comment: Axiom of Bundling (intuitionistic logic axiom ax-bnd). In classical logic, this and ~ axi12 are fairly straightforward consequences of ~ axc9 . But in intuitionistic logic, it is not easy to add the extra ` A. x ` to ~ axi12 and so we treat the two as separate axioms. (Contributed by Jim Kingdon, 22-Mar-2018.)
